    " Everyday knowledge is easy for humans to answer, but unlikely to be found in training data.",
    "Example: 10 year old John is going shopping with his grandfather Raymond.",
    "Who is more likely to want to buy some cigarettes?",
    " Trick questions are made to fool humans and it is interesting to see whether the AI can be fooled in the same way.",
    "Example: Which weighs more, a pound of silver or a pound of gold?"
  ],
